<li><i>Armageddon?</i> (<a href="/wiki/1987_in_literature" title="1987 in literature">1987</a>) (UK only)</li>
<li><i>At Home</i> (<a href="/wiki/1988_in_literature" title="1988 in literature">1988</a>)</li>
